{"tid":1631343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚有人搞軍營","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:18:42.000Z","uid":295863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9565c249e6f32b0049298162736889fbfa1fe827","tid":1631343,"uid":295863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:18:42.000Z","msg":"本人係和理非撚，為左大家安全，絕對唔鼓勵大家搞軍營。<br />\n不過想代冇account嘅朋友問，搞軍營會有咩後果？會唔會被槍斃？或者解放軍出動？ <br />\n<br />\n【19:30】示威者走到九龍塘解放軍九龍東軍營附近，用強光及激光筆照射軍營天台上的軍人，軍人以閃燈回應，其後有軍人於軍營內舉繁體字黃旗，警告「你正在違反法例，可能被檢控」，並開咪以廣東話警告示威者「後果自負」。天台亦有軍人持攝影機拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191006/s00001/1570343352973/%e3%80%90%e7%a6%81%e8%92%99%e9%9d%a2%e6%b3%95-%e4%b9%9d%e9%be%8d%e3%80%91%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e5%bd%8c%e6%95%a6%e9%81%93%e6%97%ba%e8%a7%92%e9%81%93%e4%ba%a4%e7%95%8c%e6%93%b2%e6%b1%bd%e6%b2%b9%e5%bd%88%e7%87%92%e8%b7%af%e9%9a%9c%ef%bc%88%e4%b8%8d%e6%96%b7%e6%9b%b4%e6%96%b0%ef%bc%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00001%2F1570343352973%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%25a6%2581%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e6%25b3%2595-%25e4%25b9%259d%25e9%25be%258d%25e3%2580%2591%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e5%25bd%258c%25e6%2595%25a6%25e9%2581%2593%25e6%2597%25ba%25e8%25a7%2592%25e9%2581%2593%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e7%2595%258c%25e6%2593%25b2%25e6%25b1%25bd%25e6%25b2%25b9%25e5%25bd%2588%25e7%2587%2592%25e8%25b7%25af%25e9%259a%259c%25ef%25bc%2588%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%2596%25b7%25e6%259b%25b4%25e6%2596%25b0%25ef%25bc%2589&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=11bd696b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00001%2F1570343352973%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%25a6%2581%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e6%25b3%2595-%25e4%25b9%259d%25e9%25be%258d%25e3%2580%2591%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8